        "content": "<p>&nbsp; 110. 作業一靜態陣列和動態陣列有何差異？指出其優缺點。*</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; margin-left:6.75pt; margin-right:6.75pt; width:708px\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:32px\">\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:316px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">動態陣列</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:360px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">靜態陣列</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:32px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">使用</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:316px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">初始不需要指定陣列大小，可以動態增減元素</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:360px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">須</span><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">事先宣告</span><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">陣列大小</span><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">，不能動態調整</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:32px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">優點</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:316px\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">彈性較高，可以動態調整大小</span></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">避免了固定大小可能造成的記憶體浪費</span></li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:360px\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">存取速度較快</span></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">不需要額外的記憶體管理</span></li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:32px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">缺點</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:316px\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">較靜態陣列稍慢</span><span style=\"color:#a52a2a\"> <span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">因為可能需要重新配置記憶體和複製元素</span><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">)</span></span></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">需要額外的記憶體管理</span><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">可能產生記憶體碎片。</span></li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:360px\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">建立陣列時確定大小，無法更動</span></li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">可能會造成記憶體浪費</span> <span style=\"color:#a52a2a\"><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">因為預先</span><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">設定</span><span style=\"font-family:DengXian\">了固定大小的記憶體</span><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">)</span></span></li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:32px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">例子</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:316px\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>vector &lt;string&gt; name ;</li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:360px\">\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>&nbsp;char name[100] ;</li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:32px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-family:新細明體,serif\">示意</span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align:top; width:316px\">\r\n\t\t\t<p><a href=\"/user/1/1/11127109/images/dynamics_2d_array.png\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/user/1/1/11127109/images/dynamics_2d_array%281%2